<h1><span class="guide-title">Build a</span><OutlineFilter twColor="--color-p-navy-light"><span class="guide-title guide-title-white">Space&nbsp;Shooter!</span></OutlineFilter></h1>

### What you'll have by the end of this guide

- A player spaceship that moves left and right
- Bullets that fire upward
- Enemy ships that fall from the top
- Collision detection - bullets destroy enemies
- A score counter
- A game over screen with restart

